{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_06_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 幸せにしてあげる",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ryou_living_yoru",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "僕のご飯で、誰かが幸せそうにしてるのはいいものだね\n誰かと結婚するっていうのは、こんな感じなのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing someone happy with my cooking is nice.\nIs this what it's like to be married?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、人にご飯を作ってあげるくらい\nいちいち結婚しなくても出来ると思うんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I think cooking for someone\ndoesn't require getting married.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "結婚したら、ずっと一緒にいることになるんでしょ？\nがんじがらめで息が詰まらないのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you get married‚ you're together all the time‚ right?\nWouldn't that be suffocating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7000008266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなのがずっと続いたら\n好きな相手でも、そのうち嫌いになってしまいそうだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that went on‚\nyou'd end up hating even someone you love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7666683834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも他人に、幸せにしてあげると言ってもらっても\nあまり嬉しいとは思えないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ if someone told me they'd make me happy‚\nI wouldn't be very happy about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.03333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、練習に付き合ってもらっておいて悪いけど\n脚本の台詞はどうもピンとこないんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ sorry for making you practice with me‚ but\nI can't really relate to the script's lines.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0607949485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしようか\nやっぱり、今からでも断った方がいいのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do?\nShould I just back out now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8000024796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや……その前に、さっきの葵の考え方を\nそのまま、ドラマの制作側に伝えてみるのはどうだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… before that‚ why not tell the production team\nexactly what you just told me‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1333358129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕の考え方って……ああ、結婚は息が詰まるっていう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My thoughts… you mean that marriage is suffocating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8412038486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "だって、結婚して幸せになるヒロインなんだろう？\nそんなこと言ったら、もうクビだと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the heroine is supposed to get happily married‚ right?\nIf I say that‚ I'll probably get fired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.407869498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "言ってみないと分からないけど……\nでも俺は、本音を言っている葵の顔が一番いいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won't know until you try…\nBut I think your honest expression is the best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8191065152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "向こうも、葵を気に入ってオファーしてくれたんだし\n葵のいいところを視聴者に見せたいと言えば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They liked you enough to offer you the role‚\nso if you say you want to show the viewers the real you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4999994278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……そう、うまくいくものかなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… will it really work out that way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8140554746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、ここは、君のお手並み拝見といこうじゃないか\n頼りにしてるよ、マネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let's see what you've got‚ Manager.\nI'm counting on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.047388808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 105.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 105.4666594822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――それから、しばらく経って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333353678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "葵が出演するドラマの撮影が始まった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Filming for the drama Aoi starring is in begins.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4859439531,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3014.056046899995,
          "startTime": 111.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 111.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……やっと着付けとメイクが終わった\nじっとしてるのにも飽きたよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… The fitting and makeup are finally done.\nI'm tired of sitting still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1140529314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……って、なんでまた目を丸くしてるのさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why are you looking so surprised again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8140514055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 123.7807170549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "凄い似合ってるなって……いや似合うとは\n信じてたけど、想像以上というかだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look amazing… I mean‚ I knew you'd look good‚ but…\nit's even more than I imagined…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2999979018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 132.3202091853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　ドレス風の衣装だって何度も着てるじゃないか\n白一色でここまでのボリュームはめずらしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I've worn dress-like outfits many times before.\nThough‚ it's rare to have this much volume in pure white.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4535425186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 141.6333414077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、女の人のウエディングドレスっていうのは\n迫力が違うというか、また特別というか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but a wedding dress is different.\nIt has a special presence‚ a certain impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1000080744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "そんなものかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7780862172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 151.5114114125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "ウエディングドレスなんて、重いし硬いし動き辛いし\nなんというか、全身鎧を着込んだような気分だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A wedding dress is heavy‚ stiff‚ and hard to move in.\nIt feels like I'm wearing a full suit of armor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9114114125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "よ、鎧……\nまぁでも、葵らしい感想かもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-suit of armor…\nWell‚ that sounds like something you'd say‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4666767756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 167.3000024796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "あ。そろそろ本番が始まるみたいだ\nそれじゃ、頑張って戦ってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it looks like it's almost time to start filming.\nI'll go give it my best shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9042158764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio",
      "startTime": 171.9042158764
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.1333307266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに祝福されて、君と結ばれるなんて\n思ってもみなかったから……なんだか、夢みたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought I'd be blessed by everyone and end up with you…\nIt feels like a dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.2042199454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_03-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "え……一生、僕を幸せにするって？\n嬉しいけど――でも、ちょっと違うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… you’ll make me happy for a lifetime?\nThat’s nice‚ but…――It’s a little different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1042189282,
      "sfxList": []
